                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18160110-90-off503 t18160110-90-cd504"></join>, a quantity of hemp flax and twine, value 40s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18160110-90-victim817" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Christy
                  <interp inst="t18160110-90-victim817" type="surname" value="Christy"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18160110-90-victim817" type="given" value="John"></interp>
